response.overview: December 8th, 2012 :: Combat Zone Wrestling presents Cage Of Death 14 from the Flyers Skate Zone in Voorhees Township, New Jersey, USA. Matches include:  • CZW Tag Team Title Ultraviolent Insanity Six Man Tag Team Match  4-Loco (Alex Colon, Azrieal & Bandido Jr.) (c) vs. The Nation Of Intoxication (Danny Havoc, Devon Moore & Lucky 13)  • Rich Swann vs. Shane Strickland  • Greg Excellent & Momma Excellent vs. Campaign For A Better Combat Zone (Drew Gulak & Kimber Lee)  • Sami Callihan vs. Adam Cole  • CZW Tag Team Title #1 Contendership Match  OI4K (Dave Crist & Jake Crist) vs. BLK OUT (BLK Jeez & Ruckus)  • CZW Wired TV Title Match  AR Fox (c) vs. Robert Anthony  • CZW World Heavyweight Title Match  MASADA (c) vs. Drake Younger  • Cage Of Death Match  DJ Hyde vs. Matt Tremont
response.title: CZW Cage Of Death 14
